%H A014011 Yong-Gao Chen, <a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s11425-012-4540-6">On the reciprocal sum of a sum-free sequence</a>, Sci. China Math., 56 (2013), 951-966, doi:10.1007/s11425-012-4540-6.
